                          <property name="setting_description">[B]Parallel (All Enabled Slots)[/B] runs every enabled slot at the same time — how many run is automatic (2 enabled = 2 parallel, 3 enabled = 3 parallel). Same as 1.6.0 when all slots are on.[CR][CR][B]Series (Fallback by Slot Order)[/B] is separate: runs slot 1 first, then slot 2 only if slot 1 returned no torrents, then slot 3 only if slot 2 returned nothing. Slower; useful for obscure titles or when your primary scraper often misses results.</property>
                          <onclick>RunPlugin(plugin://plugin.video.playtvban/?mode=settings_manager.set_from_list&amp;setting_id=external_scraper.run_mode)</onclick>
