                          <property name="setting_description">When enabled, Play TVBan removes one active Real Debrid torrent before adding a new one if you already have 5 active downloads (RD's usual limit). This can prevent failed resolves when slots are full, but may delete a transfer you started elsewhere — including in the RD website or another app. Leave disabled unless you often hit resolve failures due to too many active downloads.</property>
