                          <property name="setting_value">...</property>
                          <property name="setting_description">Configure automatic retries when a source search returns no playable results. Each action can be Off, Auto, or Prompt, with order from Highest to Lowest. Rescrape With No Cache Check disables per-provider external cache checks (Real Debrid, All Debrid, TorBox, Premiumize, Offcloud). Rescrape With Disabled External Providers includes disabled external torrent providers (not internal scrapers such as EasyNews or debrid cloud). Offer Full Search After Early Results applies to the empty-search retry path only; Check Before Full Search and Run External Scraper Search during prescrape are separate.</property>
                          <onclick>RunPlugin(plugin://plugin.video.playtvban/?mode=rescrape_actions_choice)</onclick>
                      </item>
